---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section
  class="py-section-padding px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-surface-container-low/50 relative"
  id="features"
>
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter items-center">
      <div
        class="md:col-span-7 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant p-10 bento-card relative overflow-hidden"
      >
        <img
          alt="Thinking Pulsi"
          class="absolute -right-8 -bottom-8 w-48 h-48 opacity-10 pointer-events-none"
          src={`${base}images/problema.png`}
        />
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-error-container/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-error" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;"
              >warning</span
            >
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg">El Problema de la Visibilidad</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-12 max-w-lg">
          Los líderes suelen detectar bloqueos y sobrecarga en los equipos cuando ya existen atrasos
          o pérdida de productividad. Pulsi anticipa estas señales dispersas.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/30 text-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary block mb-2">schedule</span>
            <span class="text-label-sm font-label-sm">Atrasos</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/30 text-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary block mb-2"
              >sentiment_dissatisfied</span
            >
            <span class="text-label-sm font-label-sm">Frustración</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/30 text-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary block mb-2">groups</span>
            <span class="text-label-sm font-label-sm">Descoordinación</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-surface rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/30 text-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary block mb-2">trending_down</span>
            <span class="text-label-sm font-label-sm">Baja Eficiencia</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
        <img
          alt="Pulsi Concerned Mascot"
          class="w-64 h-64 object-contain drop-shadow-2xl"
          src={`${base}images/problema.png`}
        />
        <div
          class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-outline-variant max-w-xs text-center"
        >
          <p class="text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant italic">
            "¿Cómo saber si mi equipo está al límite antes de que sea tarde?"
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="pulse-line"></div>
</section>
